                <h1>First-year Sanford initiative POLIS engaging students with politics</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/9291acdf-495d-48ff-8fb4-caa0b3c89e9c.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            

